data.text: Looking to hit up South Beach!? Check out our place on Airbnb for your next stay! Link can be found below! Book your next Miami getaway in this bright and lovely studio unit, steps away from Miami beach! Fully furnished and equipped with all essential items you need to make yourself at home. → Beach access is just across the street! → High-speed Wi-Fi → Has Cooler, umbrella and beach chairs available! → Fully equipped kitchen with complete set of cookware → Walk Score of 87! (dining, nightlife, cafes, shopping within walking distance) The space Here are some of the amenities this place offers you to make your stay more comfortable! → SmartTV from which you can access your Netflix or YouTube. → Studio features a cozy Queen size bed, and one blow up twin mattress → Full sets of hotel quality sheets and duvets for the beds and enough towels. Guest access Guest will have access to the entire unit. Please make yourself at home! Beach access is just across the street! Other things to note NO PARKING Please be informed that we do not have a free parking space on premise however you may use the paid parking located about 8 blocks from the apartment that will cost you $10 per day since the meter are from 8 am to 6 pm $1 a hour and free after 6 pm. Parking garage is located at 400 W42nd St. Miami Beach FL, 33140 https://lnkd.in/gFi_pvcb We do not allow baggage drop off. Licence number BTR010555-07-2021, 2371611 #miami #miamibeach #newyorkcity #canada #usa
